    "description": "Curefit Consulting Pvt Ltd invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Full Stack Developer at our Jodhpur location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Curefit Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nCurefit Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in REST APIs\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Curefit Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
